080-k-no\" alt=\"Medina Burger - Burger &amp; Sides | Casablanca\"></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"reviews\" class=\"reviews\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\">Ils en parlent</div>\n      <h2>Ce que disent nos clients</h2>\n      <p>Avis vérifiés Google — 180 retours et comptant.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rev-grid\"><div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"Thank you for the service, Meryem.\"</p><div class=\"author\">— Mohamed Amine</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"Hello, it is with great pleasure that I write these lines. An impeccable place, helpful people, especially Miss Meryam. Best of luck. Thank you.\"</p><div class=\"author\">— SAID MOUSSAID</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"I came with my husband while I was pregnant and received a very warm welcome. We ordered a Tangia burger and a Mashrum burger. A waitress named Mariam took care of us very kindly. Thank you so much, Mariam!\"</p><div class=\"author\">— Aziza Mamane</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"I came to your restaurant with my family. We ordered a Tangia burger, a truffle burger, a mushroom burger, and chicken. The meal was delicious! 😍 Your restaurant is excellent! 👌🏼 Keep up the good work! You have the best servers, especially Maryam! 👍🏼👍🏼 This young woman knows how to charm customers with her kindness and beautiful smile. Thank you to Sofia and the whole team. We will gladly return! \"</p><div class=\"author\">— malika mamane</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"Sophia and Moussa were amazing, food was amazing, atmosphere was amazing. Highly recommend this place!\"</p><div class=\"author\">— simon symth</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div><p>\"Best burger I ate in Morocco\"</p><div class=\"author\">— Florian Schmi